For nmt:

1. pull the python3-http template from ZiyunZhao's git repo. 
faas template pull --overwrite https://github.com/ZiyunZhao/python-flask-template

2. create a new python3-http template. 
faas new --lang python3-http function-name

3. modify the image path in the .yml file starting with a dockerhub username.

4. modify the requirement.txt in the folder to include the libraries you need.

5. modify the handler.py in the folder named function-name. 

6. use the up command to deploy the function. 
sudo faas-cli up -f function-name.yml

